Cls
ROBOCOPY /E /B /NC /ETA /NDL /NFL /COPYALL "C:\Users\%UserNa%\Downloads" "D:\AJQ_BackupData\Downloads"
Echo 按任意键退出...
Pause > Nul
Exit

:Bkup_Document
Cls
ROBOCOPY /E /B /NC /ETA /NDL /NFL /COPYALL "C:\Users\%UserNa%\Documents" "D:\AJQ_BackupData\Documents"
Echo 按任意键退出...
Pause > Nul
