:Bkup_DekDoc
Cls
ROBOCOPY /E /B /NC /ETA /NDL /NFL /COPYALL "C:\Users\%UserNa%\Desktop" "D:\AJQ_BackupData\Desktop"
ROBOCOPY /E /B /NC /ETA /NDL /NFL /COPYALL "C:\Users\%UserNa%\Downloads" "D:\AJQ_BackupData\Downloads"
Echo 按任意键退出...
Pause > Nul
